{"tid":2356334,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"眼帶賤種入 你而家識分顯示卡種類未","createTime":"2021-01-06T17:51:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T11:39:11.000Z","uid":143341,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"0473f7cc424c8541d53080978e4860db739650bd","tid":2356334,"uid":143341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T17:51:33.000Z","msg":"眼帶賤種你條撚樣借手足過橋食女<br />\n仲玩精神有問題會員 <br />\n冇道義又冇口齒<br />\n正一食屎狗"},{"pid":"cbd950d3d15a34c01d7c21c698f3fee9b73ed53b","tid":2356334,"uid":143341,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T17:57:57.000Z","msg":"眼帯の喰種 #284432<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n眼帯の喰種七宗罪<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">(1) 雙重標準</span></span><br />\n同樣係有user被起底，牠對於木耳同壽司郎pt仔嘅態度截然不同：<br />\n壽司郎pt被起底，keep住推再開post (2)<br />\n<br />\n木耳被起底，全程幫木耳護航，甚至不惜明明有證據就扮睇唔到，老屈：<br />\n<br />\n(a) 波台狗報國安 (事實係 時事台會員 另一個廚房 報）<br />\n(b) 木耳無用分身自己推自己<br />\n<br />\n一樣被起底，木耳有勢力有fans就幫，pt仔無人識就踩多兩腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">(2)性騷擾女user</span></span><br />\n只係見到人地隻倉鼠同一小截手指，就成副狗公格出曬嚟係到性騷擾人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GsYkmVc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGsYkmVc.png&h=a27b9038&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n改名前係感情台做狗公：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GTaF6mY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGTaF6mY.jpg&h=b75b3ba4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">(3) 周圍扮熟r frd</span></span><br />\n鍾意痴埋啲有知名度嘅會員到扮熟r frd, 結果比人笑到面黃：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ye2JjHf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fye2JjHf.png&h=0638ece4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n又試過去娛台扮熟幫印狗護航，點知娛台個個反印狗：<br />\n<br />\n友台接二連三有人出事<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2347525\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2347525</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">(4) 屈毛</span></span><br />\n完全接受唔到批評，每次同人意見相左，輕則精神勝利法block人，重則幫對方打上唔同嘅標籤（五毛pr, 波台狗, 熱狗）。唔少會員無係波台開過post都被佢打成波台狗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kpcJjHo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkpcJjHo.jpg&h=edc004ba&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ydTgEHp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FydTgEHp.jpg&h=28d656b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">(5) 欺凌精神病人</span></span><br />\n幫今日最熱門壽司郎pt post 開(2), 仲係每個回覆附上post 1 link:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E2HAVfR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE2HAVfR.png&h=27c58085&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我返Pt 今日俾壽司郎藍田店店長炒魷魚 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2354018\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2354018</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">(6) 無料扮四條 </span></span><br />\n睇唔明英文解讀錯個tweet, 比人指正就話自己ielts reading 8.5 撻人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3gKzrnC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3gKzrnC.png&h=1067d2bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">(7)吹水作故仔</span></span><br />\n自稱自己識得612 reminder admin, 但係人地admin話唔識呢個人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R5XECun.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR5XECun.png&h=63a0fc25&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O7AuZHJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO7AuZHJ.png&h=12967823&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X1FfaPp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX1FfaPp.jpg&h=1c1ba41a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M2JcXuq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM2JcXuq.jpg&h=a7b71596&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G6qrhur.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG6qrhur.jpg&h=5986a941&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sMcM1V7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsMcM1V7.png&h=0fedba03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n條友依家利用緊啲無腦黃幫佢手spin去第二度 spin成係啲波台人入嚟蓄意搞破壞 希望有腦有獨立思考嘅手足自己可以判斷下條賤種係咩人先 唔好再俾佢利用spin走曬成件事<br />\n<br />\n睇曬下面啲嘢要繼續撐嘅請各位自便 明明時事 娛樂台 硬件台 動漫台 感情台 遊戲台 app台周圍都有人屌佢 多得班人幫佢spin成做賤種俾波台惡意追擊 條友淨係夠膽覆波台人士跟住貼人係波台開過post就話人波台狗，其他台屌佢嘅一律skip<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n等多啲人睇下佢點利用手足過橋<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實佢唔係第一次 呢個post入面有部分佢言論嘅cap圖 條友最鍾意就係屈鳩人無做過或者講過嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n會員#284432眼帯の喰種(原名777傻的嗎)quit登存證區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2298808\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2298808</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n條仆街仲試過利用手足過橋flirt絲打<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V3KDbri.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV3KDbri.png&h=aeda4011&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HnndKMj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHnndKMj.png&h=87147d37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其後聲稱對方係天水圍連線區議員<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eKHk9fm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeKHk9fm.png&h=cff2474e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被flirt絲打<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EP6qAVn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEP6qAVn.png&h=955aea17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n天水圍連線區議員全為男性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[/quote]"},{"pid":"dff1fe256ab06ec7649d28234c7451cf1b51574f","tid":2356334,"uid":143341,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T17:58:44.000Z","msg":"喂 食屎狗眼帶<br />\n證據係晒到喇"},{"pid":"8a043a1b56ad8d2ff7d2ace062df83909fbc2927","tid":2356334,"uid":143341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score